13. MOST ASKED INTERVIEW QUESTIONS
===================================

13.1 What is Spring Messaging?
Unified abstraction for message-based communication.

13.2 Difference between Spring Messaging and Spring Integration?
Messaging ‚Üí core abstraction
Integration ‚Üí EIP implementation

13.3 Is Spring Integration synchronous?
| Question                                    | Answer |
| ------------------------------------------- | ------ |
| Is message payload mutable?                 | ‚ùå No   |
| Can one channel have multiple consumers?    | ‚úÖ Yes  |
| Does DirectChannel create new thread?       | ‚ùå No   |
| Is Spring Messaging thread-safe?            | ‚úÖ Yes  |
| Can Spring Integration work without broker? | ‚úÖ Yes  |

It supports both sync and async.

